  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, combine fish sauce, soy sauce, and brown sugar; stir to dissolve.",
    "In a large pot, combine ginger, cinnamon sticks, nutmeg, and star anise; cook over medium heat, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add ground pork to the pot; cook, breaking up with a spoon, until no longer pink, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add beef broth and water to the pot; bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Cook rice noodles according to package instructions; drain and set aside.",
    "To assemble the pho, place noodles in a bowl; add slices of cooked pork and ladle hot broth over the top.",
    "Serve with lime wedges and garnish with cilantro, if desired."
